From 7c1f009de18be6d66da923be63001749ecabbb2b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: regksem <regksem@tuta.io>
Date: Fri, 19 Jun 2026 18:54:39 +0300
Subject: [PATCH] Add custom MOTD support (MiniMessage, online booster, attack
 favicon hiding)

New motd section in xwaterfall.yml backed by Adventure/MiniMessage:

- protocol-version: -1 echoes the client's own protocol (never 'outdated').
- custom.motd: MiniMessage template (legacy & / section + hex auto-detected),
  with {NL}, {PLAYER_ONLINE} and {PLAYER_ONLINE_MAX} placeholders.
- custom.max-players: player count shown in the ping.
- online-multiplier: round(real online * multiplier).
- favicon-path / favicon-compression-level: configurable, re-encoded favicon.
- hide-favicon-on-attack + attack-pings-per-second: drop the favicon under a
  ping flood (AttackTracker) to save traffic.

